description: Number of triangle-free trivalent (or cubic) graphs with 2n labeled nodes.
references: R. W. Robinson, Numerical implementation of graph counting algorithms, AGRC Grant, Math. Dept., Univ. Newcastle, Australia, 1977.
N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
N. C. Wormald, The number of labeled cubic graphs with no triangles, Congress. Numerantium, 33 (1981), 359-378.
author: _Simon Plouffe_ and _N. J. A. Sloane_.
